translated: Kindberg, Karl-Gustav, Bachelor of Jurisprudence, ombudsman, Huskvarna, born on January 11, 1913 in Jönköping, son of the manufacturer C.B.K. and Anna Kindberg. Married in 1943 to Vera Edén. Children: Gunilla, born in 1945. Completed his Bachelor of Jurisprudence in 1941. Worked as an ombudsman for the Jönköping City Property Owners Association, served in various positions in institutions and private companies in Jönköping from 1930 to 1936, city notary in Uppsala in 1940, notary at a defense agency in 1941. Held various functions in the Uppsala Student Union, including being the head of the union's office, involved in international bureau activities and employment services for intellectuals from 1937 to 1939. Undertook several municipal assignments in Huskvarna from 1943.
